thread.title: BRIEF-eHealth Sees Q4 2017 Revenue Of $39 Mln To $40 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-eHealth Sees Q4 2017 Revenue Of $39 Mln To $40 Mln
text:
Jan 16 (Reuters) - eHealth Inc:
* EHEALTH, INC. ANNOUNCES PRELIMINARY RESULTS FOR THE FOURTH QUARTER AND FISCAL YEAR 2017
* SEES FY 2017 REVENUE $172.5 MILLION TO $173.5 MILLION * SEES Q4 2017 REVENUE $39 MILLION TO $40 MILLION * - ‍GAAP NET LOSS FOR Q4 2017 EXPECTED TO BE IN RANGE OF $23.5 MILLION TO $22.5 MILLION​
* Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE VIEW $-1.21, REVENUE VIEW $37.0 MILLION -- THOMSON REUTERS I/B/E/S Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
